{"word":"κατασπένδω","slug":"κατασπένδω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>κατασπένδω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-σπείσω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to pour as a drink-offering</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>libare</el>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>:—<a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a> <i>to pour drink-offerings</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a>, <el>κ. τινὰ δακρύοις</el> <i>to honour with offerings</i> of tears, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>; <el>κ. τινά</el> <i>lament with tears</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>III. </b><i>to consecrate</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}